OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,FFormer England manager Sir Gareth
OL,8,FSouthgate has revealed he has a ticket
OL,9,Flined up for the World Cup final
OL,10,Fbecause if the national side makes it
OL,11,Fthrough, he "wants to be there".
OL,13,FThe 55-year-old also said he was "not
OL,14,Fmissing" having to tell players they
OL,15,Fwere not part of the team, which he
OL,16,Frecalled were "some of the most
OL,17,Fhorrendous conversations".
OL,26,@sD@MOUsD@_O]uD@bOUvD@HO]xD@OOUyD@YO]
