OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,FSir Gareth made his comments ahead of
OL,8,FThomas Tuchel naming his 26-man squad
OL,9,Ffor this summer's shot at glory in
OL,10,FNorth America on Friday morning.
OL,12,FIt meant several players learning
OL,13,Ftheir fate the previous day, including
OL,14,Fdefender Harry Maguire, who said he
OL,15,Fwas "shocked and gutted" at being left
OL,16,Fout.
OL,26,@wD@EOUwD@XO]
