OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779429952
OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,FSir Gareth, who helmed England for
OL,8,Feight years, was taking part in an on-
OL,9,Fstage chat with former BBC boss Tim
OL,10,FDavie in Los Angeles, where he talked
OL,11,Fabout handling pressure in top-tier
OL,12,Finternational football.
OL,14,FThe event was held as part of the
OL,15,Flargest ever UK trade mission to the
OL,16,FUS, aimed at bolstering the lucrative
OL,17,Fcommercial partnership between the two
OL,18,Fnations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
