CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779429952
OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,FReferring to the calls being received
OL,8,Fby the players, Sir Gareth said: "They
OL,9,Fwere some of the most horrendous
OL,10,Fconversations I ever had.
OL,12,F"So, basically, what I'm saying is I'm
OL,13,Fnot missing any of this."
OL,15,FHe added: "I also will be giving the
OL,16,Fteam space so I'm not doing media this
OL,17,Fsummer, because I think anything I say
OL,18,Fwill be amplified, thrown at Thomas
OL,19,Fand won't help his job.
OL,26,@pD@bOUtD@AOUuD@YO]wD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
