CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779429952
OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,F"But I've got a ticket lined up for
OL,8,Fthe final, because I've waited 50
OL,9,Fyears, and if we're at the final, then
OL,10,FI want to be there for sure."
OL,12,FSir Gareth was also asked about how he
OL,13,Funexpectedly became a trend-setter
OL,14,Fduring the 2018 World Cup in Russia,
OL,15,Fwhen his sporting of a smart waistcoat
OL,16,Fat matches led to a spike in sales of
OL,17,Fthe garment.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@]O]
