OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,FThree-piece suits had been provided
OL,8,Ffor the team during the tournament by
OL,9,Fthe high street retailer Marks &
OL,10,FSpencer, which Sir Gareth hailed "a
OL,11,Fgreat British brand".
OL,13,FHe recalled: "I actually said to my
OL,14,Fson, 'Do you think I get away with
OL,15,Fjust wearing this waistcoat' before
OL,16,Fthe tournament and he said 'Yeah, it
OL,17,Flooks fine, but I don't know who you
OL,18,Fthink is going to be bothered about
OL,19,Fwhat you're wearing anyway'.
OL,26,@rD@bOUsD@TO]uD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
