OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779429952
OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,F"And, of course, by the end of the
OL,8,Ftournament, British Airways were
OL,9,Fhanding out waistcoats on the flights
OL,10,Fto Moscow."
OL,12,FEarlier in the discussion and drawing
OL,13,Fon his own experience, Sir Gareth
OL,14,Ftalked about the need to get members
OL,15,Fof the team "to buy into the
OL,16,Fexperience of playing for England, the
OL,17,Fpride of playing for England".
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@KO]wD@MOUyD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
