OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779429952
OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,FHe added: "There's commercial benefit
OL,8,Fto a player being in the England
OL,9,Fsquad, but that's not why they're
OL,10,Fcoming to play.
OL,12,F"The clubs don't really want them to
OL,13,Fcome and play, because it's just an
OL,14,Finjury risk for the clubs, frankly.
OL,16,F"But you're trying to create buy-in
OL,17,Fwith superstar talents into a team."
OL,26,@oD@KOUtD@AOUxD@AOUyD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
