OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,FHe also highlighted the importance of
OL,8,Fhaving senior players, who were also
OL,9,Fgood role models, such as captain
OL,10,FHarry Kane, and challenging squad
OL,11,Fmembers who stepped out of line by
OL,12,Fkeeping them on the bench when
OL,13,Fnecessary.
OL,15,FSir Gareth also spoke about his own
OL,16,Fpart in setting an example for
OL,17,Fyoungsters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
