OL,3,CSouthgate has ticket lined up for
OL,4,CWorld Cup final in case England go
OL,5,Cthrough
OL,7,FHe said: "The reason I coached wasn't
OL,8,Fto just win football matches, I wanted
OL,9,Fto help people improve, learn, be the
OL,10,Fbest version of themselves. That's the
OL,11,Fbit that I really loved working with
OL,12,Fplayers on, so that applies across any
OL,13,Fyoung person."
